{"id":752,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":752,"title":"Isaiah 50","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 50"],[".studySummary",["i","Isaiah speaks as the Messiah—He will have the tongue of the learned—He will give His back to the smiters—He will not be confounded—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7"},"2 Nephi 7"],"."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1","order":"02.24.050.49080"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Thus"],"saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Where",["i","is"],"the bill of your mother’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"divorcement"],", whom I have put away? or which of my creditors",["i","is it"],"to whom I have sold you? Behold, for your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"iniquities"],"have ye sold yourselves, and for your transgressions is your",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"mother"],"put away."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.2","order":"02.24.050.49081"},["b","2"],"Wherefore, when I came,",["i","was there"],"no man? when I called,",["i","was there"],"none to answer? Is my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"hand"],"shortened at all, that it cannot redeem? or have I no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"power"],"to deliver? behold, at my rebuke I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"dry up"],"the sea, I make the rivers a wilderness: their fish stinketh, because",["i","there is"],"no water, and dieth for thirst."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.3","order":"02.24.050.49082"},["b","3"],"I clothe the heavens with blackness, and I make sackcloth their covering."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.4","order":"02.24.050.49083"},["b","4"],"The Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"hath given me the tongue of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"learned"],", that I should know how to speak a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"word"],"in season to",["i","him that is"],"weary: he wakeneth morning by morning, he wakeneth mine ear to hear as the learned."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.5","order":"02.24.050.49084"},["b","5"],"¶The Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"hath opened mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"ear"],", and I was not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"rebellious"],", neither turned away back."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6","order":"02.24.050.49085"},["b","6"],"I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"gave"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"back"],"to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"smiters"],", and my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"cheeks"],"to them that plucked off the hair: I",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"hid"],"not my face from",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_6f"},"shame"],"and",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_6g"},"spitting"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.7","order":"02.24.050.49086"},["b","7"],"¶For the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"will help me; therefore shall I not be confounded: therefore have I set my face like a flint, and I know that I shall not be ashamed."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.8","order":"02.24.050.49087"},["b","8"],["i","He is"],"near that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"justifieth"],"me; who will contend with me? let us stand together: who",["i","is"],"mine adversary? let him come near to me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.9","order":"02.24.050.49088"},["b","9"],"Behold, the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"will help me; who",["i","is"],"he",["i","that"],"shall condemn me? lo, they all shall wax",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"old"],"as a garment; the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"moth"],"shall eat them up."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10","order":"02.24.050.49089"},["b","10"],"¶Who",["i","is"],"among you that feareth the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that obeyeth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"voice"],"of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"servant"],", that walketh",["i","in"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"darkness"],", and hath no",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"light"],"? let him",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"trust"],"in the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_10f"},"stay upon"],"his God."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.11","order":"02.24.050.49090"},["b","11"],"Behold, all ye that kindle a fire, that compass",["i","yourselves"],"about with sparks: walk in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"light"],"of your fire, and in the sparks",["i","that"],"ye have kindled. This shall ye have of mine hand; ye shall lie down in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sorrow"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1a","order":"02.24.050.49091"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/7.1.1-11"},"2 Ne. 7:1 (1–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1b","order":"02.24.050.49093"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abrahamic-covenant"},"TG Abrahamic Covenant"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/divorce"},"Divorce"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1c","order":"02.24.050.49095"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.1d","order":"02.24.050.49097"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.2"},"Hosea 2:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.2a","order":"02.24.050.49099"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.1"},"Isa. 59:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.8"},"D&C 35:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.2b","order":"02.24.050.49101"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.67"},"D&C 133:67"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.2c","order":"02.24.050.49103"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/drought"},"TG Drought"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.4a","order":"02.24.050.49105"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.15.14-15"},"Luke 21:15 (14–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.4b","order":"02.24.050.49107"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/25.11"},"Prov. 25:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.5a","order":"02.24.050.49109"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.1"},"D&C 58:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.5b","order":"02.24.050.49111"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.39"},"Matt. 26:39"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.8"},"Philip. 2:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6a","order":"02.24.050.49113"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-condescension-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Condescension of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6b","order":"02.24.050.49115"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6c","order":"02.24.050.49117"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.4.1-12"},"Isa. 53:4 (1–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.26"},"Matt. 27:26"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6d","order":"02.24.050.49119"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.30"},"Lam. 3:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6e","order":"02.24.050.49121"},["b","6e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"},"TG Jesus Christ, Exemplar"],"."],["div",{"id":"6f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6f","order":"02.24.050.49123"},["b","6f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"6g","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.6g","order":"02.24.050.49125"},["b","6g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.67"},"Matt. 26:67"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.8a","order":"02.24.050.49127"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.32.32-34"},"Rom. 8:32 (32–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.9a","order":"02.24.050.49129"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.6"},"Isa. 51:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.16"},"D&C 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.9b","order":"02.24.050.49131"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.8.7-8"},"Isa. 51:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10a","order":"02.24.050.49133"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.38"},"D&C 1:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10b","order":"02.24.050.49135"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/servant"},"TG Servant"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10c","order":"02.24.050.49137"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10d","order":"02.24.050.49139"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"10e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10e","order":"02.24.050.49141"},["b","10e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.116"},"D&C 84:116"],"."],["div",{"id":"10f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.10f","order":"02.24.050.49143"},["b","10f"],["span.small","HEB"],"be supported by."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.11a","order":"02.24.050.49145"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/50.11b","order":"02.24.050.49147"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"TG Sorrow"],"."]]}
